        </Number><Title>Income and capital</Title><Chapter DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2012/319/part/6/chapter/6" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2012/319/part/6/chapter/6" NumberOfProvisions="7" id="part-6-chapter-6" RestrictStartDate="2013-01-28"><Number>CHAPTER 6</Number><Title>Capital</Title><P1group RestrictStartDate="2013-01-28"><Title>Capital limit</Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2012/319/regulation/40" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2012/319/regulation/40" id="regulation-40"><Pnumber>40</Pnumber><P1para><Text>No person is entitled to council tax reduction if that person's capital exceeds £16,000.</Text></P1para></P1></P1group></Chapter></Part></Body></Secondary></Legislation>